BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:-Q2sdMTnA5zjU25Xfk-Up
SUMMARY:Mary Jane: Preview Performance
DTSTAMP:20260315T002144Z
DTSTART:20260320T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:Poignantly humorous and deeply cathartic\, this semi-autobiogra
